The '''White Knights' Castle Crypt''' is a crypt found beneath the [[White Knights' Castle]]. Its entrance can be be found in the south-western corner of the yard of the castle. The crypt, where the [[White Knights]]' greatest knights are buried{{CiteNPC|npc=Squire (Crypt)|quote=The greatest White Knights are buried here, after a lifetime in the service of Saradomin.}}, is being cleaned (or rather: supposed to be cleaned) by the squire [[Vicks]], and contains a portal to [[Death's Office]].
